    <briefdescription>
<para>Hit detector helper class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The hit detector class compare measurement data in z direction against threshold and count the number of hits. It provides a method to identify a hit and store it in a private couter variable, a method to retrieve the number of hits and a method to reset the counter variable. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
